data.description: Nestled In The Serene Location Of Almo, Kentucky, 206 Metcalf Lane Offers A Perfect Retreat For Those Seeking Rural Living. This Charming Property Boasts A Picturesque Setting, Fenced In Back Yard, Comfortable Living Spaces, Large Kitchen Area, And Ample Outdoor Opportunities. With 3 Bedrooms, 2.5 Bathrooms, And An Array Of Modern Amenities, All While Being Miles From Town, This Home Has It All.
